          <title>
            <string language="en">Replica plating of bacteria</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Repliküberzug des Bakteriums</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Électrodéposition de reproduction des 
bactéries</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Chapeamento do replica das bactérias</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Placcatura della replica dei batteri</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Επένδυση αντιγράφου των βακτηριδίων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Laminado de la reproducción de bacterias</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the replica plating of bacterial colonies growing on plates containing ampicillin onto plates containing tetracycline.</string>
          </description>
          <language>x-none</language>

            <string language="en">bacterial colonies</string>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt den Repliküberzug der 
bakteriellen Kolonien, die auf den Platten wachsen, die Ampicillin auf
die Platten enthalten, die Tetracyclin enthalten.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre l'électrodéposition 
de reproduction des colonies bactériennes accroissant des plats 
contenant l'ampicilline sur des plats contenant la tétracycline.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra o chapeamento do replica
das colônias bacterianas que crescem nas placas que contêm o 
ampicillin nas placas que contêm o tetracycline.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra la placcatura della 
replica delle colonie batteriche che crescono sulle piastre che 
contengono l'ampicillina sulle piastre che contengono la tetraciclina.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει επένδυση αντιγράφου των 
βακτηριακών αποικιών που αυξάνεται στα πιάτα που περιέχουν 
ampicillin επάνω στα πιάτα που περιέχουν tetracycline.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra el laminado de la 
reproducción de las colonias bacterianas que crecen en las placas que
contienen la ampicilina sobre las placas que contienen el 
tetracycline.</string>
          </description>
